  <summary date="2024-01-25T14:12:24Z" status="Introduced in House">Stop Anti-Semitism on College Campuses Act

This bill prohibits an institution of higher education (IHE) that participates in federal student aid programs from authorizing, facilitating, providing funding for, or otherwise supporting any event that promotes anti-Semitism on the IHE's campus.</summary>
